### Hadith 2:521

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

The Prophet said, "When a woman gives in charity from her house meals in
Allah's Cause without spoiling her husband's property, she will get a
reward for it, and her husband will also get the reward for his earnings
and the storekeeper will get a reward likewise."

